= Robotrek (SNES) - Items =

This page documents all items in Robotrek (USA version).

'''Data Status:''' Item names verified from ROM at $01e413. Stats are TBD pending research.

== Overview ==

Robotrek features 83 unique items used by the protagonist and their robots. Items are stored in the ROM as CC-terminated ($cc) strings, with a separate pointer table for quick lookup during gameplay. The item system supports equipment, consumables, key items for story progression, and materials used in the invention system.

